# LN invoice decoder

import { DecoderPage } from '/src/components/DecoderPage';

<DecoderPage />

<br />

Using the [bolt11 nodejs package](https://www.npmjs.com/package/bolt11) in the browser.<br />
The destination node data is queried from the [mempool.space API](https://mempool.space/docs/api/rest#get-node-stats).
